===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A member of an [[ancient]] northern [[Germanic]] [[tribe]] that invaded [[England]], together with [[Angle]]s and [[Frisian]]s, about the year 600.
# A [[native]] or [[inhabitant]] of [[Saxony]].
